---
import TrustLayout from '@layouts/TrustLayout.astro';
---

<TrustLayout
  title="Privacy - TEEI Trust Center"
  description="How TEEI protects and handles your data in compliance with GDPR and other privacy regulations."
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
      Privacy
    </h1>

    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
      How we protect and handle your data in compliance with GDPR and other regulations.
    </p>

    <section aria-labelledby="principles-heading" class="mb-12">
      <h2 id="principles-heading" class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
        Privacy Principles
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
            Data Minimization
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            We collect only the data necessary to provide our services and deliver value to our users.
            Personal information is limited to what's essential for impact measurement and reporting.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
            Purpose Limitation
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Data is used solely for the purposes disclosed at collection. We do not sell or share
            personal data with third parties for marketing purposes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
            Transparency
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Clear communication about what data we collect, why we collect it, and how it's used.
            Users have full visibility into their data processing activities.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
            User Control
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Users maintain control over their data with rights to access, correct, delete, and export
            their information at any time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="gdpr-heading" class="mb-12">
      <h2 id="gdpr-heading" class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
        GDPR Compliance
      </h2>

      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">
          Your Data Rights
        </h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          <li><strong>Right to Access:</strong> Request a copy of your personal data</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Rectification:</strong> Correct inaccurate or incomplete data</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Erasure:</strong> Request deletion of your personal data</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Portability:</strong> Export your data in a machine-readable format</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Restrict Processing:</strong> Limit how we use your data</li>
          <li><strong>Right to Object:</strong> Object to certain types of data processing</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-lg border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-800">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2">
            To exercise any of these rights, contact our Data Protection Officer:
          </p>
          <a
            href="mailto:privacy@teei-platform.com"
            class="inline-flex items-center text-primary hover:underline font-medium"
          >
            privacy@teei-platform.com
          </a>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-3">
            We will respond to all requests within 30 days as required by GDPR.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="data-processing-heading" class="mb-12">
      <h2 id="data-processing-heading" class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
        Data Processing & Storage
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Data Residency</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-3">
            Customer data is stored in the region specified in your contract:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <li>EU customers: Frankfurt, Germany (AWS eu-central-1)</li>
            <li>UK customers: London, UK (AWS eu-west-2)</li>
            <li>US customers: Virginia, USA (AWS us-east-1)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Retention Policies</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-3">
            Data retention periods by category:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <li>User profiles: Duration of account + 30 days</li>
            <li>Impact metrics: 7 years (for audit and compliance)</li>
            <li>Logs and analytics: 90 days</li>
            <li>Backup data: 30 days</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Data Categories</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-3">
            We process the following categories of data:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            <li>Identity data (name, email, user ID)</li>
            <li>Company and organization data</li>
            <li>Impact measurement data (SROI, VIS scores)</li>
            <li>Volunteer activity data (anonymized)</li>
            <li>Usage and analytics data</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="cookies-heading">
      <h2 id="cookies-heading" class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
        Cookies & Tracking
      </h2>

      <div class="card">
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
          We use essential cookies to maintain your session and provide core functionality.
          All analytics cookies require explicit consent.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Essential Cookies</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
              Required for authentication and session management. Cannot be disabled.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Analytics Cookies</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
              Help us understand usage patterns and improve the platform. Opt-in only.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</TrustLayout>
